          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/50e4a1f850c11d2b25d1d006760be5b8_4440361139639713716.png",
                "id": "talent9311",
                "key": "水有常形",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水有常形"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>本角色<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">附着水元素</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">化海月</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/b33ca2371d6c02d581a1a89570bc6fb8_1903076403131754252.png",
                "id": "talent74947",
                "key": "海月之誓",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "海月之誓"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，治疗所有我方角色1点，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">仪来羽衣</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/88072335/47fcf95dc439392467286728a046b049_2055699568794019249.png",
                "id": "talent60587",
                "key": "海人化羽",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "海人化羽"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，治疗我方出战角色1点。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6138612002473863139.png",
                "id": "talent94637",
                "key": "化海月",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/0e046eb8f7da357cc6b2ee42e058526a_2970105610158058275.png",
                "title": "化海月"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/88072335/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_343432524552916843.png",
                "id": "talent39941",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">附着水元素</span></strong></p><p>不通过伤害附着水元素时，发生的元素反应会忽略伤害效果：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：没有效果</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：没有效果</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绽放</span>：生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span>]</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">仪来羽衣</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">普通攻击</span>造成的伤害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附属角色普通攻击后：</span>治疗所有我方角色1点。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/28/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8112557306920465689.png",
